{"meta":{"title":"修曦","subtitle":"修身的修，美好之曦","description":"修曦的个人博客","author":"Xi","url":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs","root":"/jtgs/"},"pages":[{"title":"","date":"2023-06-22T06:52:33.097Z","updated":"2023-06-22T06:49:10.430Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":"修身的修，美好之曦曦是美好，是灵魂与心灵的火；是道与理，是永恒与希望的光。成长星火，打造曙光 喜欢的可以给个赞赏哦~"},{"title":"所有分类","date":"2023-06-18T12:06:45.166Z","updated":"2023-04-15T07:06:56.000Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"所有标签","date":"2023-06-18T12:06:45.167Z","updated":"2023-04-15T07:07:53.000Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"不该做的事","slug":"不该做的事","date":"2023-04-16T00:24:58.000Z","updated":"2023-04-16T02:12:34.000Z","comments":true,"path":"posts/643b405a.html","link":"","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/posts/643b405a.html","excerpt":"","text":"熬夜不睡觉(23点前要睡觉)懒床不起床(8点前要起床)起床不吃饭(起床稍稍做半个多小时就要去吃饭，不能8点30都没吃饭)中午不午睡(不能做着做着就忘记午睡了)午睡不起床(不能一直懒床，半小时内要起床)金刚长寿功不记得练(7点半之前起床练金刚功，晚上记得练长寿功，不想做事的时候可以多练练，做感兴趣的事多半会忘掉，也要抽空练）手机一直玩(有时候什么都不想做，不想学习也不想做想做的事，就会用玩手机逃避，但是不能一直玩，心底有四分不安就不能玩了，去喝水、练功、洗澡、睡觉、做杂事、做简单的事)一直不学习，不看论文(再不看导师问进度看你怎么办哼，每天还是要抽时间看论文啦，最少一个小时行了吧，三个小时才符合心理预期的说，七个小时才是应该的，但最少一个小时行了吧，乖哦）","categories":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"},{"name":"不该做","slug":"事情/不该做","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E4%B8%8D%E8%AF%A5%E5%81%9A/"}],"tags":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/tags/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"}]},{"title":"想做又不想做的事","slug":"想做又不想做的事","date":"2023-04-15T15:12:43.000Z","updated":"2023-04-16T01:57:17.000Z","comments":true,"path":"posts/643abeeb.html","link":"","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/posts/643abeeb.html","excerpt":"","text":"学做饭ai唱歌整理电脑手机信息等写博客看可话共鸣(483条没看了唔)发布AI画画(也有好多没发布了)整理书籍笔记等等整理自己的理论和想法未完待续","categories":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"},{"name":"想做&不想做","slug":"事情/想做-不想做","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E6%83%B3%E5%81%9A-%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E5%81%9A/"}],"tags":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/tags/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"}]},{"title":"放松或养生的事","slug":"放松或养生的事","date":"2023-04-15T14:58:46.000Z","updated":"2023-04-16T01:57:44.000Z","comments":true,"path":"posts/643abba6.html","link":"","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/posts/643abba6.html","excerpt":"","text":"洗澡喝水金刚功长寿功晒太阳、晒被子睡觉听深深唱歌未完待续","categories":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"},{"name":"放松||养生","slug":"事情/放松-养生","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE-%E5%85%BB%E7%94%9F/"}],"tags":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/tags/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"}]},{"title":"想做的事","slug":"想做的事","date":"2023-04-15T14:56:02.000Z","updated":"2023-04-15T15:19:05.000Z","comments":true,"path":"posts/643abb02.html","link":"","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/posts/643abb02.html","excerpt":"","text":"看小说轮滑ai画画未完待续","categories":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"},{"name":"想做的","slug":"事情/想做的","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E6%83%B3%E5%81%9A%E7%9A%84/"}],"tags":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/tags/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"}]},{"title":"要做的事","slug":"要做的事","date":"2023-04-15T14:53:20.000Z","updated":"2023-04-15T15:18:40.000Z","comments":true,"path":"posts/643aba60.html","link":"","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/posts/643aba60.html","excerpt":"","text":"看论文复现代码学驾照未完待续","categories":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"},{"name":"要做的","slug":"事情/要做的","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E7%9A%84/"}],"tags":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/tags/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"}]},{"title":"碎片整理计划","slug":"碎片整理计划","date":"2023-04-15T08:48:39.000Z","updated":"2023-04-25T05:09:37.000Z","comments":true,"path":"posts/643a64e7.html","link":"","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/posts/643a64e7.html","excerpt":"","text":"今年是过去和未来的衔接和转折，需要把过去的东西整理好，轻松地迈向未来。整理主要有以下内容： 1.小时候的经历照片2.过去的经历总结3.高中的作文4.大学时期的想法5.看过的好看的书籍主要是遍历现存资料，包括纸质和各种网盘、账号、存储设备中的内容。然后是还未忘却的记忆。在整理过程中也要看向未来，每天用不低于一个小时、最好三个小时时间看论文。也要做好现在，好好生活，坚持练功。","categories":[{"name":"计划","slug":"计划","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/"},{"name":"碎片整理","slug":"计划/碎片整理","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/%E7%A2%8E%E7%89%87%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86/"}],"tags":[{"name":"计划","slug":"计划","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/tags/%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92/"}]}],"categories":[{"name":"事情","slug":"事情","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/"},{"name":"不该做","slug":"事情/不该做","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E4%B8%8D%E8%AF%A5%E5%81%9A/"},{"name":"想做&不想做","slug":"事情/想做-不想做","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E6%83%B3%E5%81%9A-%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E5%81%9A/"},{"name":"放松||养生","slug":"事情/放松-养生","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%BE-%E5%85%BB%E7%94%9F/"},{"name":"想做的","slug":"事情/想做的","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E6%83%B3%E5%81%9A%E7%9A%84/"},{"name":"要做的","slug":"事情/要做的","permalink":"https://xiuxi1.github.io/jtgs/categories/%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85/%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E7%9A%84/"},{"name":"